text: Irina Turundayevskaya (born 4 February 1947) is a Soviet alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Alpine skiers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint Petersburg
title: Irina Turundayevskaya
